      "title": "Colombo in thousands - three armed forces for protection",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Thousands of people are slowly coming to Colombo city for the massive protest movement organized today (09th).",
        "Due to non-operation of public transport services, people are coming to Colombo through various modes of transport.",
        "In support of the protest, shops have been closed in some towns across the island. In the meantime, to ensure safety"
      ],
